title: Is it a Baddie or Betty?
description: Another update on how everyone's doing learning Dave's passions, Carson calls in with his own birthday song, we talk to John Reinke from Tiger King about the show, Carole Baskin, and life after blowing up on Netflix, Dave's sisters have been leaving him voicemails so we checked them, War of the Roses, and more!
